OVER THE UK ON FRIDAY WITH A WEAK LOW FLN OVER SCANDINAVIA. LOW DEEPENS SLTLY
TO 988 AS MOVS SLWY SE TOWARDS NERN UK DURING SATURDAY. LOW THEN FILLS 991
AS IT MOVS E OVER SCANDINAVIA ON SUNDAY. NEW AREA OF LOW PRESSURE 1001 DEVELOPS
OVER BAILEY ON MONDAY MORNING. STRG WINDS POSS IN FORTH FM MIDDAY SATURDAY
AND ALSO IN FORTIES TYNE DOGGER AND GERMAN BIGHT FM SATURDAY AFTERNOON.
STRG WINDS ALSO EXP IN S UTSIRE AND FISHER FM MIDNIGHT SATURDAY AND INTO
SUNDAY MORNING. GALES EXP IN FORTIES FORTH TYNE DOGGER GERMAN BIGHT AND
HUMBER FM SUNDAY MORNING. GALES CEASING FOR ALL AREAS APART FM DOGGER AND
